column2: "[Double]"

"Fufu...haha...ahahaha!
We see, we see,
so that was it...!"
"Is something funny?"

"This is something to be laughed at.
I mean, are you two trying to be ARKS?"

"ARKS... Haha... you're just ARKS,
and you're trying to embrace that much darkness."
"Shut up..."

"We finally understand after fighting.
You've already absorbed both
[Elder] and [Loser]'s power."

"That's why... even after eating them,
we couldn't become the [Profound Darkness]."

"We get it, we get it,
we really get it. Then, a reward from me."
"I'll give you me."
"That one came? Well, either one works."

"Yeah, either one's good.
You or me, whoever died,
the result would be the same."

"At any rate, it's complete.
Now, it's finished...
Fufu, fufufu, fufufufufu..."
"Congrats, congratulations. Welcome home..."
"[Profound Darkness]"
"<%me>! The result Xiao said!?"
"No, you can't! <%me>! That's not your duty!"
"That... that's... that's my responsibility! So...!"
"White Tin Clarissa! Lend me your power!"
"To save... my most important... the person I love!"

"It's okay, it's okay now.
You're tired, aren't you?
Take a good rest."
"I'm sorry..."
"<%me>! Matoi!"
"Aah, Sara... can I leave <%me> to you?"
"Matoi...!"
"Sorry... it was just as Xiao said. Xiao... He was right."
"I think I'm done for. Nothing can be done, I think."
"But... it's okay. I've done so many of the things I've wanted to do."
"You... Your memories... returned..."
"Big sister!"
"...! Aah, that's it. Sara, you're the girl from that time."

"Fufu, that's good...
You've become so pretty...
I had some regrets about you,
you know?"
"That doesn't matter at all! We need to save you...!"
"I've worked so hard to do just that... for this to happen twice...!"
"That's right. It's painful for it to happen twice, but it's okay."
"This big sister... is protecting you all."
"<%me>. Thank you."
"I've received so much, so many precious things from <%me>."
"I alone am enough. It's enough, so..."
"Goodbye."
